Mutane sama da miliyan 20 sun shaida shaidar da ta yi mamaki a ranar Alhamis ta dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da yin lalata da ake zargi da ita a shekarun 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da rikice-rikicen siyasa, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye da suka katse al'ada na karshe na ranar Jumma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
