Kavanaugh, a cikin bayaninsa, ya ce 100% ba zai faru ba.
Zai yiwu mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a suna kallon shi.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige yawan masu sauraro a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
