Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta fitar da lokutan ambaliyar ruwa na ranar Litinin da Talata don yammacin Arizona zuwa kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, da Salt Lake City.
