Shugaban Mexico, AMLO ya yi alkawarin ba zai yi amfani da sojoji ba a kan fararen hula
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai yi amfani da sojoji a kan fararen hula ba yayin da kasar ke gabatowa da cika shekaru 50 da ramuwar gayya da aka yi wa dalibai.
AMLO ta yi alkawari a Plaza Tlatelolco a ranar Asabar cewa ba za ta taba amfani da sojojin ba don ta hana 'yan Mexico.
Sojoji sun harbi fararen hula da ke zanga-zangar a cikin plaza a ranar 2 ga Oktoba 1968 wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar fararen hula 300 yayin da ƙungiyoyin ɗaliban hagu suka fara tashi a duk faɗin Latin Amurka.
AMLO ta yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga waɗanda ke koyo da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun damar ilimi na janyo hankalin matasa su shiga cikin 'yan bindiga.
Amurka ta bukaci ta ninka kudaden da ake kashewa na kera makamai
"Amurka ta bukaci ninka kudaden da ake kashewa a fannin ilimin kere kere saboda kasar Sin na kara samun karfin aiki a fannin", in ji mai zuba jari da kuma mai amfani da ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee wanda ya yi aiki a Google da Microsoft da kuma Apple.
Wannan ra'ayi ya bayyana ne bayan gwamnatin Amurka ta sanar da cewa za a yi amfani da fasaha ta wucin gadi duk da cewa Amurka kanta ba ta da wata dabarar fasaha ta wucin gadi.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da aikinta a bara tare da niyyar zama na farko a cikin sabbin abubuwan kere kere na wucin gadi ta shekarar 2030.
"Bayan an samu karin sabbin abubuwan da ake amfani da su wajen gudanar da bincike a kan ilimin kere kere, wannan kyakkyawan farawa ne, domin sauran kasashen duniya sun fi Amurka baya, kuma muna son samun ci gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji Lee.
Ta hanyar ninka kudaden zai iya kara damar samun babban ci gaban ilimin kere kere (AI) a Amurka, Lee ya ce a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Littafin Lee mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and New World Order  ya fito ne a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcout wanda shine Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures wanda ya yi zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a kan wani tsarin ilimin kere kere wanda ya rinjayi wani dan wasan Amurka mai suna Othello wanda ya kasance a matsayi mafi kyau yayin da yake karatu a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon. Daga baya, ya zama mai gudanarwa a Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban Google na China.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka ta baya kamar ta Robot Challenge daga Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Kwarewar Tsaro kuma yana son sanin lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba don ya iya gano sabbin baiwa.
"Masu bincike a Amurka suna bukatar su yi aiki tuƙuru don su samu taimakon gwamnati", in ji Lee.
