Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wani gaggawa taron jama'a a yammacin yammacin Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne taron farko na Trump daga cikin biyar da aka shirya a makon gobe, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da an dakatar da kuri'un tabbatarwa don ya zabe don cike gibin a Kotun Tarayya, Trump yana nufin samun goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar watan gobe saboda Republican yana cikin haɗarin rasa ikon Kongress lokacin da aka yanke shawarar zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare kuma yaya kuke kallon shi a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling a West Virginia an shirya shi ne da karfe 7 na dare, ET a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai iya magance shari'ar wannan makon na dan takarar kotun tarayya Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tashin hankali kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da amincewar zaben Majalisar Dattawa wanda ake sa ran za a tsare shi na mako guda yayin binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan taro mai gaggawa shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu karbuwa a zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce taro biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa zai kasance da matukar muhimmanci ga masu sa kai da magoya bayan su domin 'yan Republican suna kokarin kare da kuma bunkasa rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Shugabancin majalisar wakilai yana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa na aiki wanda shugaban kasa zai je jihohi da dama a cikinmu zuwa lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da aiki", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump da ba a bayyana sunansa ba ya shaidawa Reuters.
An shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na dare zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma janyo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, " a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne za a yi wa Trump ziyara a karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata a West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da ya kada a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke bin sa a zaben.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya tallafa masa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
