Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo, Kit Harington ya lalata namiji mai guba
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai don matsayin jarumin takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin jerin abubuwan da suka faru na HBO na wasan kwaikwayo na tsakiya, Game of Thrones.
Amma wannan dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi watsi da halinsa na jarumi mai tsananin ƙarfi, yana cewa yadda yake nuna kansa a kan allo yana nufin cewa matasa suna jin cewa suna bukatar su zama masu ƙarfi don a girmama su.
A wata hira da ta yi da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
