HIV/AIDS: Sin ta samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, jami'an lafiya sun ce.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka suna kamuwa da jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A wasu lokatai, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon zubar da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya ƙaru zuwa mutum 100,000.
Yaduwar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
A shekarar 1997, cin zarafin 'yan luwadi ba laifi ba ne a kasar Sin, amma ana ganin cewa nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi ya zama ruwan dare.
Domin tsaron kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suka yi jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
