A ranar Asabar, wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ya yi tir da zargin da wani ma'aikacinsa ya yi na wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu sanatocin 'yan Republican na Amurka a shafin Wikipedia na majalisar dokoki.
'Yan jam'iyyar Democrat na Los Angeles sun ce 'yan kungiyar 'yan ultra-right' da kuma shafukan yanar gizo ne suka yada wannan ikirarin.
Waters ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Zama, zamba da kuma wasu munanan zamba".
Wannan bayanin da aka yada ya hada da adireshin gida da lambar waya na Sanatan Amurka Lindsey Graham daga South Carolina, da kuma Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wani baƙon ya watsa su a kan Capitol Hill yayin sauraron majalisar dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan sanarwa ta fito ne bayan da Sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton adiresoshin IP da ke gano tushen aikawa da ke da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma suna yada bayanan ma'aikatan Waters, in ji Hill.
