Jihohi 18, Washington ta amince da sabon tsarin mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma yankin Columbia sun goyi bayan yin adawa da manufofin Amurka da ke hana mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga hare-haren kungiyoyin masu ta'addanci ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da yankuna sun yi rajistar abokansu a kotun a ranar Jumma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke adawa da wannan manufar, in ji NBC News.
Cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Kotu ta gabatar da ta a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya ba a bayyana ba.
Ya ce, matarsa da 'yan ta'adda sun sace shi amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da takardar neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara na jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda suka fi yawan masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin kasa da ke cike da matsalolin kungiyoyi masu aikata mugunta da kuma tashin hankali a gida.
Sabon tsarin neman mafaka na Amurka ya mayar da wani hukunci da aka yanke a shekarar 2014 inda hukumar da ke kula da masu neman mafaka ta ba da izinin 'yan gudun hijira da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida su nemi mafaka.
Karl Racine, Babban Mai Shari'a na Columbia a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a ya ce sabuwar dokar ba ta karya dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa da suka wanzu shekaru da dama da suka gabata.
Dokar tarayya ta bukaci dukkan aikace-aikacen neman mafaka su yanke hukunci bisa ga abubuwan da suka faru da kuma yanayin da suka kai ga aikace-aikacen, kuma hana su zai keta wannan ka'idar, a cewar bayanin da aboki ya yi wa kotun.
