Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da yin ta'addanci
Wata mako bayan wani jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa a cikin jaridar Amurka mai dauke da takarda hudu da ke nuna kyakkyawar yarjejeniyar cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi kasar Sin da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada propaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi magana ne game da wani talla da aka biya na China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya bayyana abin da jami'an Amurka suka ruwaito wa Reuters a matsayin sabon mataki a yakin neman neman kasar Sin.
Kasancewar al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallatawa don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington yanzu suna cikin mummunan yakin kasuwanci tare da ɗora haraji kan shigo da su.
Mataki na farko da kasar Sin ta dauka a yakin cinikayya shi ne ta kai wa masu fitar da kaya a jihohi kamar Iowa baya ga jam'iyyar Republican da Trump ke wakilta, in ji masana kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, wanda shi ne mafi yawan masu fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce matakin da Beijng ya dauka ya shafi ma'aikata da manoma da kuma harkokin kasuwanci na Amurka.
Kasar Sin, a cewar wani jarida a cikin Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi ta rubuta, "Yanzu ta fi yin lalata da yin tallan tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu ta 'yanci.
A cikin gabatar da wannan gabatarwar, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta amince da 'yancin da Amurka ke yi, al'adar da ta fi fifita 'yancin magana da' yancin' yan jarida, in ji Branstad.
A maimakon haka, a cikin jaridu a Beijing, akwai ƙarancin muryoyin adawa kuma ba za ku iya ganin ainihin ra'ayin jama'a game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba saboda kafofin watsa labaru suna ƙarƙashin iko mai ƙarfi na Jam'iyyar Kwaminisancin Sin, ya rubuta.
Ya kuma kara da cewa wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta yi watsi da tayin buga labarinta, ko da yake bai bayyana wane jarida ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da mata a zaben da suka yi a gaban 'yan majalisar saboda labarin Kavanaugh, masu bincike sun yi gargadi
Duk da cewa yawancin manyan 'yan Republican sun goyi bayan kuma sun goyi bayan Brett Kavanaugh dan takarar Kotun Tarayya wanda ke fuskantar zargin cin zarafin jima'i, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su yi kira ga amsa musamman daga mata, a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Akwai babban motsin rai a cikin wannan labarin kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun ce a cikin rikodin su za su ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya canja irin wannan yanayin ba", in ji Grant Reeher, wani farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Cibiyar Nazarin Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar a jaridar The Hill.
Reeher bai tabbata cewa matakin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya dauka na tilasta wa FBI ta fara bincike ya isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a ba.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a jiya ba - ba za su manta da gobe ba kuma ba a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kasa ga kungiyar masu cigaba ta MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington D.C.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ta ihu a lokacin da suke zanga-zangar a cikin ginin majalisar dattijai lokacin da jam'iyyar Republican da ke mulkin kwamitin shari'a ta zaɓi ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Democratic ambition da motivation za su yi fashewa", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai bincike na siyasa mai zaman kansa ga shafin labarai.
Mutane suna cewa wannan abu ne mai girma; gaskiya ne.
Wannan zai iya zama mafi girma musamman ga mata masu jefa kuri'a daga karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, 18-29 shekaru, wadanda ba sa son shugaban kasa kuma ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a.
Kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin jima'i da ake zargi da shi a kotun tarayya, masu bincike sun yi zaton za a yi alfahari da shi idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da hakan.
"Wannan ya zama wani abu mai matukar rikitarwa ga 'yan GOP", in ji Micheal Steela, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar labarai na NBC.
"Ba wai kawai zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma zaben karshe ko kuma idan Kavanaugh ya yi nasara a matsayin alkali na tarayya, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican ke magance matsalar da kuma yadda suke bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ga wani rahoto.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amirka sun rabu biyu kuma ba su san wanda za su amince da shi ba a shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh tare da fiye da rabin goyon bayan Ford.
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 sun ce za su amince da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce za su amince da Kavanaugh ko kuma za su amince da shi.
A wani lokaci kuma kashi 38 cikin 100 sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh na iya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a shaidarsa, yayin da kashi 30 cikin 100 ne kawai suka yi hakan game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya yi watsi da shi, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma akalla wani zargin, in ji Deborah Ramirez, jaridar The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata Ford ya yi ikirarin rantsuwa a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya zarge shi a lokacin da yake da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya kuma ce dan takarar kotun tarayya ya nuna rashin kunya a gaban Ford a wani biki yayin da yake karawa a Jami'ar Yale a cikin shekarun 1980.
Masu kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya suna shirin kaddamar da sabuwar hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo don hada Google da Facebook
Wanda ya kirkiro Yanar Gizo na Duniya, Tim Berners-Lee ya kaddamar da wani kamfani na farko don ya yi gwagwarmaya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon shiri na wannan sanannen fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ke amfani da software na Open Source na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai sami damar samun damar bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa ainihin manufar Inrupt ita ce domin mamaye duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi haka yanzu", in ji shi game da wannan kamfani.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid wanda ke bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar bayanan sirri na kan layi na kansu ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyukan yau da kullum, kalandar, jerin waƙoƙi da sauran kayan aikin ƙwararru na sirri.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify wanda za'a iya samu a cikin burauzar guda daya kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da adana bayanai a cikin wannan tallan na sirri shi ne cewa ya dogara ne da mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar irin bayanan da ake buƙata.
Kamfanin ya bayyana shi a matsayin mai sarrafa kansa ta hanyar bayanai.
Wannan burin Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shi ne ya kawo wasu albarkatu, matakai da kwarewa don taimakawa mutane su ji dadin Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikatan ci gaba da aka yi wa kwangila don yin aiki a kan wannan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kyauta na codebreaking.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasaha daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu ba tare da kasancewa a kowane wuri ba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya kuma ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da sauyi inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su zai canza nan take.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A cikin wata sanarwa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Bernes-Lee ya rubuta, Inrupt, saƙon sa shine samar da makamashi ga kasuwanci da kuma yanayin halittu don taimakawa kare intergridity da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina ta amfani da Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza duniyar Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya yi muhawara sosai game da bukatar samun 'yanci a yanar gizo.
Yayin da yake kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da kuma Daraktan Consortium na World Wide Web, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An yi bikin girmamawa ga Fasto mai karɓar Victoria Cross na Yaƙin Duniya na Farko
Firist na Ikilisiyar Ingila ne kawai ya karbi lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin soja ya yi bikin a cikin ƙauyen bayan shekaru 100.
Lt. Col. Father Benard Vann wanda ya karbi wannan lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba 1918 a hare-haren Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi ne ta hanyar bindiga kwana hudu bayan haka kuma ba tare da sanin cewa ya san cewa an ba shi babbar lambar yabo ta sojojin Birtaniya ba.
An kafa wani abin tunawa kuma manyan jikoki biyu sun bude wajansa a wani gangami a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce wannan alama ce mai ban mamaki domin dutsen zai buɗe shinge shekaru 100 bayan babbansa ya yi wannan aikin.
A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya kai batalolinsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin wanda ya cika da hazo mai zurfi kuma ya kewaye da babban hari na mashin.
Sai ya yi ta harbi zuwa iyakar kasar kuma ya yi gaba gaɗi sosai kafin ya yi amfani da bindigarsa ya harbi mutane uku.
Wani dan Jamus ya kashe Lt. Col. Col. a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918 - wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, 72, ya ce babbansa ya yi wani abu da ba zan iya maimaitawa ba kuma yana da ban sha'awa.
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma sa wasu furanni bayan wannan bikin da Brentwood Imperial Youth Guard ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce an girmama shi sosai don ya kasance cikin wannan al'umma kuma ya kara da ƙarfin hali ga goyon bayan da mutane da yawa suka bayar.
