Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa wani sabon rikodin a ranar Lahadi a lokacin da ya buga karo na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup, amma dole ne ya kasance a shirye ya biya kuɗin wasan don kada ya ƙare cikin baƙin ciki.
Mickelson wanda zai taka leda a wannan shekara ta biyu a matsayin mai rikodin sau 12, ya yi wa kyaftin din Jim Furyk ja-gora don wasan fourballs da foursomes a ranar Asabar.
Duk da cewa sun kasance a cikin al'ada a Amurka, masu cin nasara a manyan wasanni biyar sun ciyar da lokaci suna yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma horarwa da fatan za su inganta ingancin wasan.
Wanda ba zai iya buga kwallon kai tsaye ba ko da a lokacin da yake kan gaba, dan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shine mafi kyawun zaɓi don filin golf na Le Golf National ba, inda nisa mai nisa yana da matukar wahala ga bugun da bai dace da manufa ba.
Idan filin golf ne kawai zai sa ya yi wuya, Mickelson a wasan tara na ranar Lahadi zai yi karo da wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin Birtaniya, Francesco Molinari wanda ya shiga tare da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanni hudu na makon nan.
Idan dan wasan Amurka ya ci gaba da wasa guda hudu a wasanni 12 na farko, da farko da karfi, to, wasan Mickelson ya kasance da matukar muhimmanci.
Furyk ya amince da 'yan wasansa sosai, shi ne kawai zai iya cewa.
"Ya fahimci matsayinsa na yau, kuma ya yi ta yi mini duka ta'aziyya, ya kuma sa hannunsa a kafaɗata ya ce zai kasance a shirye a gobe", in ji Furyk.
