Sabbin jiragen yakin Jamus sun yi jinkiri kuma
Rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta bukaci ta karbi sabon jirgin ruwanta a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a kammala jirgin ba har sai shekara mai zuwa saboda lalacewar tsarin da kuma karuwar farashin, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
A halin yanzu an dakatar da binciken jirgin ruwan Rhineland-Pfalz, wanda shine na farko a cikin nau'in Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates, har zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit wanda ya yi magana da kakakin soja.
Wannan jirgin ya kamata ya shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma rashin alheri bayan mika wuya ya sa aka yi watsi da wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da aka ba da umarnin Navy a 2007 za su maye gurbin Bremen-class frigates.
An san cewa zai ƙunshi siffofi kamar manyan bindigogi masu ƙarfi, kayan aiki na anti-ship da anti-ship da kuma wasu siffofi na ɓoyewa kamar rage radar, fitilun ja da kuma ikon sauti.
Wani muhimmin abu kuma shi ne tsawon lokacin kiyayewa - wannan sabon jirgin ruwan dole ne ya iya yin tafiya har zuwa shekaru biyu daga lokacin da ya tashi.
Duk da haka, wannan babbar jirgin ruwa mai mahimmanci wanda aka ce zai iya nuna ikon Jamus a ƙasashen waje - zai zama tsoho ne a lokacin da jirgin ya shiga aikin Navy, a cewar Die Zeit
Wannan jirgin F125 mai saukin kai ya zama sanarwa a bara, lokacin da jami'an sojin ruwa na Jamus suka ƙi amincewa da jirgin kuma suka mayar da shi ga kamfanin Blohm & Voss na Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Sojojin Sojoji suka mayar da jirgin ga masu gininsa bayan an kai shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka dawo da jirgin ba, amma jaridu na Jamus sun ce wasu lalacewar software da na'urori sun sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi don aikin yaƙi.
Ana bukatar a yi la'akari da lalacewar software domin jiragen yakin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class za su yi aiki da makamai 120 kawai - rabin abin da ake bukata don sarrafa tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Ka kuma nuna cewa jirgin ya yi nauyi sosai kuma hakan zai rage aikin da kuma iyakance ikon da rundunar ta ke da shi na yin wani ci gaba a nan gaba.
Jirgin saman Rheinland-Pfalz 7,000-tan an yi imanin ya ninka nauyin jirgin saman saman saman da aka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga lalacewar na'urar, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ƙwararrun - kuma batun ne.
An ce aikin ya kai €3.1 biliyan ($3.6bn) - ya karu daga farashinsa na asali na €2.2 biliyan.
Matsalar da ta afku a kan wannan sabon jirgin ruwan ya nuna yadda sojojin Jamus ba su da karfin yin aiki.
A farkon wannan shekara, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar ya amince da cewa sojojin ruwa suna fama da matsalar rashin jiragen ruwa masu iya aiki.
Jami'in ya kuma ce matsalar ta kara muni, saboda tsoffin jiragen da aka dakatar ba su da wani jirgin da za su maye gurbinsa.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
