Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa garin Palu a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi, adadin mutuwar ana sa ran zai karu.
Da rashin samun damar sadarwa, hukumomi ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, yankin arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa da girgizar ƙasa mai girma 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala yanki ne na 300 km (180 mil) a gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan yanki, yanki na yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Fishing da kiwo sun zama tushen tattalin arzikin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin ruwa na Donggala.
Ana kuma yin hakar nickel a yankin, amma ana yin hakan ne a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha Tsumani sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100, a cewar Hukumar Rashin Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Fire Circle kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai girma a yammacin yankin Acheh, Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a duk faɗin ruwan Tekun Indiya, rabin adadin a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane daruruwan sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da Kota Padang, babban birnin yankin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, a Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami har zuwa mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai matsakaici ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Acheh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, tunatar da mazauna taron manyan lalacewar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a shekara ta 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka yi a lokacin, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
