Masu gabatar da kara sun bukaci hukuncin kisa mai tsanani ga wadanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na New York sun bukaci hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas -- hukuncin kisa wanda ba a yi ba a jihar da ake kira tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, 30, an zarge shi da amfani da wata babbar motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Avenue a Lower Manhattan, yana mamaye matafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a kan titin a ranar Oct.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "ya yi niyyar" kashe wadanda suka mutu takwas da kuma "ya yi niyyar" yin mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da ke nufin neman hukuncin kisa, a cikin fayil a Southern District, New York.
An yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan tuhuma biyu, a cewar takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da tuhuma 22 ciki har da zargin kisa takwas saboda ayyukan haramtacce, wanda masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motocin mota.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "tsabtace shiri da kuma shiri" wanda, a cewar masu gabatar da kara, ya bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan harin a matsayin "mai laifi, mai zalunci da kuma wulakantacce".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, zafi, da rashi", a cewar wata sanarwa da niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe matafiya ne daga Argentina.
Kusan shekaru da yawa ne da suka gabata, Kananan Hukumomin Kudancin New York sun yi ikirarin kisa.
An zargi mai kare, Khalid Barnes, da kisan gillar 'yan kasuwa biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa na karshe a wani karamin shari'ar tarayya a New York, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An yanke wa Rosenberg hukuncin kisa ta hanyar yin amfani da kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, ya samu kansa a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Ya bayyana wa masu binciken cewa yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya ce an tilasta masa ya kai hari ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon da ake yi wa kungiyar ta ISIS a wayar, a cewar zargin.
Ya kuma bukaci a saka tutar ISIS a cikin dakunan asibiti, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan zargin 22 da aka yi masa.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin yaki na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Mun ji cewa hukuncin neman kisa ya fi karbar karbar hukuncin rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba, yana ƙara wa duk waɗanda suka yi abin da ya faru wahalhalu", in ji Patton.
Masu kare Saipov sun bukaci masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
