Yaƙin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya amfanar Beijing
Fashewar da aka yi a farkon yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China na iya zama abin damuwa, kuma ko da yake har yanzu ba a kammala yakin ba, rikice-rikice tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya amfanar Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Donald Trump, shugaban Amurka, ya ba da gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekara ta hanyar sanya haraji kan fitar da kayayyakin kasar Sin ciki har da wutar lantarki, baƙin ƙarfe da aluminum.
Mafi yawan karin kudade ya faru ne a wannan makon tare da sabon kudade wanda zai shafi dala biliyan 200 na darajar kayayyaki, wanda zai shafi haraji a kan rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta yi daidai da yadda ta yi a duk lokacin da ta yi amfani da haraji na 5 zuwa 10 bisa dari a kan kayayyakin Amirka biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta biya wa Amurka duk wani abin da ta yi, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu mafi girma ba ya jin dadin hakan.
Sa Washington ta koma baya yana nufin ta yi biyayya ga nufin Amurka, amma ta yi biyayya ga Amurka yana da matukar kunya ga Shugaba Xi Jinping na kasar Sin.
Masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da kyau, to, da matsa lamba daga yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafa wa kasar Sin a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin kasashen biyu.
"Shakamakon gaggawa na siyasa na ko Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da rashin kulawar tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa kuma yana da alama ya fi haɗari fiye da abin da masu lura suka sani a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, wani bincike mai mayar da hankali ga Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta New America, wani rukuni na masu tunani.
Syria ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar siyasa, Ministan Harkokin Wajen ya ce
Syria ta ce ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar siyasa da son rai kuma ta nemi taimako wajen sake gina kasar da yaki na shekaru bakwai ya hallaka.
Da yake jawabi a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce, halin da ake ciki a kasar ya inganta.
"Yanzu halin da ake ciki a kasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali, godiya ga ci gaba da aka samu wajen yaki da tashin hankali", in ji shi.
Gwamnati za ta ci gaba da mayar da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka hallaka don dawo da su cikin al'ada.
Yanayin yanzu yana shirye don komawar 'yan gudun hijira, zuwa ƙasashen da suka bar saboda tashin hankali da matakan tattalin arziki na gefe guda da ke shafar rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da kuma wuraren da suke nema.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan kasar Syria miliyan 5.5 sun tsere tun lokacin da yaki ya fara a 2011.
Mutane miliyan shida da suka rage a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimakon da ake bukata don sake gina wannan kasa mai lalacewa.
Amma ya tabbatar da cewa kasar ba za ta karbi taimako ko taimako daga kasashen da ke goyon bayan tawayen ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke Ƙungiyar Amurka ta ƙarshe da maki 16.5, 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka yanzu ta sha kashi shida a jere a ƙasar Turai kuma ba ta lashe Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin lokacin da tawagar Captain Denmark, Thomas Bjorn ta samu 14.5 da ake bukata don kayar da Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, ya yi gwagwarmaya a duk lokacin wasan, ya jefa tee a cikin ruwa a cikin par-3 rami na 16, ya mika wuya ga rashin nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
'Yan wasan golf na Italiya sun yi fice a duk zagaye, suna daya daga cikin' yan wasan hudu da suka kasance 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya fito a 5&4 da dan wasan da ya fi tsayi a Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, babban dan wasan duniya, ya fadi zuwa 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga wasan Ryder Cup na karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup na takwas, dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai na tsawon lokaci tare da maki 25.5.
"Na yi kuka da wuya amma ba zan iya jurewa a yau.
Wannan shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas ya zaɓe ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki sosai, ina farin cikin samun lambar yabo.
Wannan ga tawagar ce, kuma ina farin cikin taimakawa", in ji Garcia bayan cin nasarar Turai.
Ya mika aikin ga John Ram wanda ya doke almara na Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasa daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Na yi alfahari da ganin yadda na ci Tiger Woods, kuma na yi girma da ganin yadda yake wasa.
Woods ya sha kaye a duk gasar da aka yi a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 na Ryder Cup.
Wani mutum mai ban mamaki da ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya 14 ya yi nasara a kan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya a ƙarshen mako don neman hanya, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka buga wasan golf mai kyau a duk lokacin wasan.
Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan da tawagarsa ta yi takaici, "Ina alfahari da su, suna aiki tuƙuru.
A wani lokaci da safiyar yau mun ba da kayan aiki ga ƙungiyar Turai.
Mun yi iya ƙoƙarinmu.
Na gode da wannan, Thomas.
Ya kasance kyawawan kyaftin.
Dukkan 'yan wasan 12 da ya buga sun yi kyau sosai.
Za mu sake haduwa, zan yi aiki tare da PGA of America da kuma Ryder Cup Committee kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama kyaftin.
Dole ne ku ɗaga hatsi.
Mun yi nasara".
